            </div>
            <hr>
            <div class="col-sm-3">
               <div class="profileimage" style="margin-left:-20px;margin-top:15px;"><img style="height:200px; width: 120px" src="/img/volunteer1.jpg">
               </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-8">
               <h3 style="margin-top:10px;"><a href="/volunteer/emma">Emma</a></h3>
               <h6 style="line-height:22px;color:#292929;font-size:14px;">Educator and mother dedicated to supporting her community. Emma believes that each member of a community brings a unique talent to improving and transforming a community. As a Volunteer Coordinator, Emma is one of the original members of Search who continues to... <a href="/volunteer/emma"> Learn More.</a></h6>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
   </div>
</div>
<script>
   $('.carousel').carousel({
    interval: 4000
   });
</script>